掛替身，得天國之眼DIO更外掛先贏到<br />\n波波：銀震<br />\n轉靈魂，再殺（DIO實戰智商=on99）"},{"pid":"da3c4597986e4e929081b253052da5b018094d75","tid":1287590,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7672c66a6345c9b2d8dc5dbc3dabb0be00b2232","tid":1287590,"uid":159997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"普奇神父：白蛇、天堂製造（加速中後期）<br />\n白蛇攞CD、天堂製造中後期飛刀殺（承太郎打佢唔死）<br />\n岸邊露伴：天堂之門<br />\n扮路人突擊、令佢無法直接或間接傷害岸邊露伴<br />\n老闆：緋紅之王<br />\n時閃爆頭<br />\nGioGio：黃震<br />\n無敵外掛替身，得天國之眼DIO更外掛先贏到<br />\n波波：銀震<br />\n轉靈魂，再殺（DIO實戰智商=on99）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:41:22.000Z","msg":"*註：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=9up<br />\n<br />\n承太郎：白金之星/白金之星世界<br />\n唔需要解釋<br />\n艾梅斯：親吻<br />\n用硬物障礙夾柒DIO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五部肥仔：惡名昭彰的B.I.G<br />\nDIO實戰=on9 個替身可以吸生命、再生"},{"pid":"c678b9d479b42c144f0a28f771c08ba80dde64c9","tid":1287590,"uid":159997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"福葛：紫煙<br />\n唔知DIO可唔可以抵禦致命生化病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究極卡茲：無替身<br />\n波紋勁過Joseph幾十倍同埋飛行速度追到戰鬥機<br />\n布加拉提：sticky finger<br />\n攬炒肉搏將DIO斬件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nVanilla Ice: 亞空瘴氣<br />\n時停最多可以避 如果vanilla ice唔突個頭出黎 DIO無辦法傷害佢 吸血鬼應該唔會餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三部食屎細路：死神<br />\n唔知DIO會唔會訓覺、訓前應該唔會啟動替身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n億泰：The Hans<br />\n可以消除DIO個頭，不過本體唔係戰鬥天才<br />\n吉良吉影：殺手皇后/穿心攻擊/敗者食塵<br />\n搵個路人設炸彈再逼個路人講佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n穿心攻擊應該唔得，因為DIO可以玩冰<br />\n總統：D4C<br />\n搵個廢啲平行宇宙既DIO黎殺（例如SBR前期Diego)殺完之後搵DIO送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5aafdc24de81e624a183cbfa2c945cb1c809b20","tid":1287590,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"波因哥：托托神<br />\n跟足故事書預言既指示黎做一定贏，除非荒木改劇本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n康一：回音act2<br />\n寫「陽光」落DIO度/附近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n噴上裕也：高速之星<br />\n無弱點既替身，DIO行路同飛天應該都無60km/h掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加埋佢有令隧道變裡空間既能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（後期荒木沒收左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\nGioGio：黃金體驗<br />\n用左一次就俾荒木沒收左既精神暴走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9248c8aa8bcdff1f963a2b0c7fd00761617e7a","tid":1287590,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"我感覺我既解釋開始牽強到好似李斯咁既地步<br />\n波爾波： 黑色安息日<br />\nDIO只可以夜晚出擊，夜晚黑色安息日有影，任意出現，射程大，同埋DIO唔會發現鋪床係替身使者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住黑色安息日磨死DIO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChocolata: green day<br />\n引DIO中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第六部自虐狂：highway to hell<br />\n開槍爆自己頭<br />\n天氣：天氣預報<br />\n將DIO變蝸牛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第六部懲教佬：流浪之星<br />\n日頭用隕石炸爆DIO大宅，令陽光燒死DIO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n凡蘇思：地底世界<br />\n夜晚引DIO出街打、再重演日頭有陽光既一件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nJohnny: tusk act4<br />\n無限力量迴轉轉鳩DIO<br />\n林果：mandom<br />\n時間倒退六秒，可不斷loop。只要DIO無辦法秒殺佢，佢就可以loop爆DIO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n露伴番外篇幅畫<br />\nDIO一睇到幅畫就必死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd4a3cc69029b1f6e71a9874732be4495c77dead","tid":1287590,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"over heaven<br />\n完"}]}